# ── Obsidian Portable binaries (large; distribute separately as .zip/.7z) ───
ObsidianPortable/App/Obsidian/
ObsidianPortable/App/Obsidian64/
ObsidianPortable/App/Bin/
ObsidianPortable/ObsidianPortable.exe
ObsidianPortable/Other/
ObsidianPortable/help.html

# ── Runtime data generated by Obsidian / Electron ───────────────────────────
ObsidianPortable/Data/ObsidianAppData/
ObsidianPortable/Data/settings/
ObsidianPortable/Data/PortableApps.comInstaller/

# Vault content — not part of this repo (user data)
ObsidianPortable/Data/Obsidian Vault/

# ── Patched .rdp files that contain real credentials ────────────────────────
# Keep the template; ignore any copies that carry a real password blob.
Инструкция/*.local.rdp
scripts/*.local.rdp

# ── Do not commit a copy of the patch script with real secrets ───────────────
# (the committed version has empty CONFIG fields)

# ── OS / editor artefacts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.lnk

# ── Windows temp / log leftovers ─────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
